The President of the United States had a meeting with His Highness Salman bin Hamad Al Khalifa, Crown Prince of Bahrain. They discussed Bahrain's commitment to reform and the importance of both the opposition and the government compromising for a just future for all Bahrainis. The President emphasized the need for accountability for human rights abuses and stated that the stability of Bahrain depends on respecting the rights of the people and implementing meaningful reform.